features: ❐「Modern Tree Bookshelf」Give Up the Bulky and Traditional Bookcases! Inspired by Tree Branches, We Design the Bookshelf in a Tree Shape, Cleverly Combining Practicality and Aesthetics. Being Placed in Home, Books on the Shelf Are Like Abundant Fruits and the Bookcase is Like a Living Tree That Grows Upward.

❐「Large Storage Bookcase」This Geometric Bookshelf Has 9 Spacious Shelves Offering Ample Amount of Storage Space Capabilities. Sturdy Enough to Hold All Kinds of Books and Magazines to Fit Everywhere. It Can Hold About 5-10 Books Per Shelf.

❐「Space-Saving Corner Shelf」Without Occupying Too Much Space, Its Vertical Design Makes It More Suitable for Small Place Storage. Make Rooms Well Organized Instead of Being in a Mess. Simple Yet Functional Enough to Decorate Your Home. Made of Solid and Thick Boards, This Bookshelf is Sturdy and Will Provide Long Time Service. There is Also an Anti-toppling Device at Back to Add More Security.

❐「Versatile Application」Perfect for Use in the Living Room to Display Family Albums or Other Favorite Collections, Working in Offices to Store Books, File Folders, and Other Decorative Stuff, Also Perfect in Kids' Room to Organize Photo Albums and Books.

❐「Easy to Assemble」With the Detailed Assembly Manual and Numbered Parts, It is Easy for You to Assemble This Tree Bookshelf and a Possibility to Restore a Tidy Home. the Storage Cabinet Can Be Suitable for Various Styles of Home Decoration, Adding a Touch of Elegance to Your Space.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Value for money
reviews.reviewText: Very easy to assemble, looks great and helped to organize my books while not taking up a lot of space. Very sturdy in the design. Would order again

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Don't Buy Boring Bookshelves
reviews.reviewText: I have two of these now - one on each side of the fireplace. They hold my favorite books and they are super fun to look at. I bought one from another company before finding this one. They are both the same quality and this one was a much better value. It does take some time to put them together - pay close attention to the instructions - but it wasn't hard as long as I stayed focused and didn't try to rush it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice, inexpensive, initially a bit unstable and flimsy
reviews.reviewText: The instructions are obviously for someone who has experience with these type of shelves or IKEA style furniture. However, once you do one the remaining are easier (assuming you get more than one).However, as others have mentioned, the are a bit flimsy and potentially unstable. Granted there is a single point mounting screw to attach this to the wall, however, as it becomes weighted down the security of this shelf becomes questionable. (Lots of books, earth tremors, climbing cats, etc.)I wound up designing and 3D printing a decent reinforcement bracket that aligns with the securing mount screw but adds a lot more stability and reduces the flimsiness. It can be found at ' printables<<dot>>com '. Search for ' Wall Bracket for Function Home Tree Bookshelf '. You can print this yourself or have a local 3D print shop do it for you.Now I have no worries about rambunctious kids and cats, mild quakes or over stuffing the shelves.

reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Pretty bookcase, just not very sturdy
reviews.reviewText: It definitely leans forward a bit. If you don’t have lot of books (or heavy) to put on this, then perfect. It does come with one of those screws you can use to attach to the wall, but that might be a bit more iffy if you’re renting.
